l="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131205494,imgsize-101616.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Fashion giant 'Mango' founder Isak Andic’s son arrested over tycoon’s death in 2024]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131204663.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Spanish police arrested Jonathan Andic, son of late Mango founder Isak Andic, in connection with his father's December 2024 death. Initially ruled an accident, the case reopened after inconsistencies in Jonathan's testimony emerged. Family sources express full confidence in his innocence, awaiting further investigation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/fashion-giant-mango-founder-isak-andics-son-arrested-over-tycoons-death-in-2024/articleshow/131204663.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/fashion-giant-mango-founder-isak-andics-son-arrested-over-tycoons-death-in-2024/articleshow/131204663.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T20:48:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131204850,imgsize-729907.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Manhole death in NYC: Straight from her Mercedes-Benz, woman falls into uncovered sewer hole]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131204793.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/manhole-death-in-nyc-straight-from-her-mercedes-benz-woman-falls-into-uncovered-sewer-hole/articleshow/131204793.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/manhole-death-in-nyc-straight-from-her-mercedes-benz-woman-falls-into-uncovered-sewer-hole/articleshow/131204793.cms]]></guid><pubDate>202