s.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-student-dies-in-road-accident-in-australia-was-hit-and-trapped-under-a-car/articleshow/131202787.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T19:12:52+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131202853,imgsize-125182.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[$200 million kitty: Meet Choupette, the world's richest cat, whose lifestyle would make Cleopatra envious]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131202292.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[But even the lower reported number is staggering. If one uses the $1.5 million figure and compares it with the median net worth of an American family, about $192,900 in the most recent Federal Reserve survey, Choupette’s supposed care arrangement works out to roughly 7.8 times that figure. Round it off, and the headline becomes irresistible: this cat may be worth eight times the typical American family. If one uses the higher $4 million rumour, the number rises to about 20.7 times the median American family net worth.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/200-million-kitty-meet-choupette-the-worlds-richest-cat-whose-lifestyle-would-make-cleopatra-envious/articleshow/131202292.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/200-million-kitty-meet-choupette-the-worlds-richest-cat-whose-lifestyle-would-make-cleopatra-envious/articleshow/131202292.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T18:59:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131202420,imgsize-16148.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who were Cain Clark and Caleb Vazquez? San Diego mosque shooter's mother called police hours before attack]]></t